414
00:23:46,809 --> 00:23:49,343
Edna, it's bill.
Oh?

415
00:23:50,912 --> 00:23:52,546
Hello, sweetie.

416
00:23:52,548 --> 00:23:53,781
No.
No sign of them yet.

417
00:23:53,783 --> 00:23:57,551
We're beginning to suspect that Harry took
