Go back to sleep.

465
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:27,868
Is he a babysitter?
Gee whiz!

466
00:26:27,870 --> 00:26:30,337
Never mind now.
Go to bed.

467
00:26:30,339 --> 00:26:33,974
Oh, uh, these are my sons,
Larry and Tony.

468
00:26:33,976 --> 00:26:36,076
